{
  "ninemarchesStart": {
    "class": "StartEvent",
    "properties": {
      "text": "You set foot on the Nine Marches, the vast accursed continent east of Nouraajd. The plague-cult of Marumi Baso works toward the Ninefold Crowning - to raise a dead god by digging up its grave-crown from the Cyclopean Citadel at the heart of the world. From the crossroads town of Gravewatch, the marches spread out in every direction: the Reaved Fields, the Plague-Fen, the Barrowlands, the Ashmarch, the Drowned Coast, and the Cold Reach. Gather the keys, read the obelisks, and reach the Citadel before the cult crowns its king."
    }
  },
  "gravewatchSign": {
    "ref": "signPost",
    "properties": {
      "text": "GRAVEWATCH - crossroads of the Nine Marches. Roads: Fields (here), Fen (west), Barrows (north), Ashmarch (east), Cold Reach (far north), Drowned Coast (far south-east). Beware the deeper marches."
    }
  },
  "citadelSign": {
    "ref": "signPost",
    "properties": {
      "text": "THE CYCLOPEAN CITADEL - seat of the Ninefold Crowning. The grave-crown lies beneath. Read all six obelisks, or the ground will not give up its king."
    }
  },
